     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * PARAMETER                                        *
      *   IN                                               *
      *      PIPGMN : PROGRAM NAME (CL)                    *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PIPGMN 10
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      * UNLOCK
     C           PIPGMN    CHAINAPLPP801             21
